reviewText: Bobbikins was released in 1959. It starred Shirley Jones. A cute story about a taking baby. I saw this in the theatre. Fans of Shirley Jones will like this the most.
Such a cute little musical movie!
I love old movies and was happy with the quality.

Another letterboxed film, original ratio 2:35 to 1...released as a full frame dvd.  Haven't they learned by now yet? Well, I guess not, because one of the characteristics of being an idiot is NOT KNOWING you're an idiot, and Fox sure meets that definition.  Fail.  No sale.
